      "review_summary": "The branch changes Control UI chat session select rendering, mobile selector CSS/classes, and chat view tests to keep fallback active sessions selected after rerender.\n\nReproducibility: yes. at source level and with inspected screenshots. Current main still uses attribute/default selection in the active shared renderer, and the PR media shows the selector/thread mismatch before the branch and aligned state after it.",
